{"tid":823104,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[災後救援] 動物收容所義工召集","createTime":"2018-09-16T15:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T02:13:35.000Z","uid":118161,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"938648c8aaeb7491b45c0849b2183f8cae7f72b5","tid":823104,"uid":118161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T15:58:22.000Z","msg":"RCAP拯救遺棄寵物中心因為打風水浸，場內幾百隻狗受影響，幸運地場內的水已經退了。現需要大量義工及舊毛巾替毛孩冲涼，否則會有皮膚病。<br />\n <br />\n有興趣做義工可pm或留tg，會約埋喺西鐵站一齊去，無經驗唔緊要，大家請有心理準備，路封左，車行不到，要步行入，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n地點：流浮山上白泥31 號<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/131565040224459/posts/1777571038957176/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F131565040224459%2Fposts%2F1777571038957176%2F&d=Ca0vyMdcXwcQhBZMct%2BZAV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=bf455911\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/131565040224459/posts/1777571038957176/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/16/235701_ee53a441260727c73603790e644efe25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F16%2F235701_ee53a441260727c73603790e644efe25.png&h=9a499028&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a363054b6f2d9041380f54adcf320c6c10675bdb","tid":823104,"uid":50779,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a66b9d5c1a13c4336bf6fdd2ffb6d8fa250dbb7","tid":823104,"uid":68632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:02:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35adba154dc0cc0b1833b1100ee8da45487b5aff","tid":823104,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:07:24.000Z","msg":"聽日得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496f7ec697eaf2bc60cddd02d1e313960a6f9add","tid":823104,"uid":174979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:18:30.